    <item>
      <title>Sequence</title>
      <link>https://beardog-ukr.github.io/cocos2dx-examples/en/post/basic-sequence/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Sep 2020 15:05:25 +0300</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://beardog-ukr.github.io/cocos2dx-examples/en/post/basic-sequence/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you need to perform few actions one by one over the same object you can use the &lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.cocos2d-x.org/cocos2d-x/v4/en/actions/sequences.html&#34;&gt;Sequence&lt;/a&gt; class.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For example the blue ship in our &lt;a href=&#34;https://beardog-ukr.github.io/cocos2dx-examples/en/post/basic-actions/&#34;&gt;previous demo&lt;/a&gt; appears to be facing north. If we want it to fly to the right we should first rotate it by 90 degrees and then perform the move.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
